maintext:
INDIANAPOLIS (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday afternoon’s drawing of the Indiana Lottery’s “Quick Draw Midday” game were:
01-05-06-13-15-30-38-40-45-46-47-55-62-67-68-69-72-76-77-78, BE: 72
(one, five, six, thirteen, fifteen, thirty, thirty-eight, forty, forty-five, forty-six, forty-seven, fifty-five, sixty-two, sixty-seven, sixty-eight, sixty-nine, seventy-two, seventy-six, seventy-seven, seventy-eight; BE: seventy-two)
